# =============================================================================
# Docker Build Exclusions — STUB ONLY
# =============================================================================
#
# This file is intentionally a stub. ``docker-compose.yml`` sets
# ``context: ..``, so Docker reads ``.dockerignore`` from the *project
# root*, NOT from this directory. Edits here have no effect on the build
# image.
#
# To change what is excluded from the Docker build context, edit
# ``../.dockerignore`` (the project-root file). This stub is kept only
# so contributors who instinctively look in ``docker/`` see this notice
# instead of silently editing a dead file and believing the change
# applies.
#
# Cross-reference: ../.dockerignore is the authoritative exclusion list.
# =============================================================================
